						<summary>

						<p>This records the construction of the entrance and the <hi rend="italic">gōpura</hi> of the temple of Tāntōṉṟi-Āḷuḍaiyanāyanār at Śaṇbai <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vīrarājēndraśōḻapuram in Vāṇagōppāḍi by Vaḷavaṉ Pallavaraiyaṉ Maṇḍaippiḷḷai, Vijayarāyaṉ, the headman of Kurugāḍi in Tenkiḻā-nāḍu, a division of Nittavinōda-vaḷanāḍu (See No. 99 above).</p>						

